{"tid":1962181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"據統計至少19個國家首名確診病人來自武漢","createTime":"2020-04-07T09:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T18:18:19.000Z","uid":125168,"like":437,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"21e291e6a36fb8e92159fdca7233c2ef7e3d20a7","tid":1962181,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"至少19個國家首名確診病人來自武漢<br />\n<br />\n蘋果全文：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200407/H6RWFYR624CTNSA4V47PIKXUG4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2FH6RWFYR624CTNSA4V47PIKXUG4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=98b69731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2FH6RWFYR624CTNSA4V47PIKXUG4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=0b662404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200407/H6RWFYR624CTNSA4V47PIKXUG4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200406/large/1586186987_b1a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200406%2Flarge%2F1586186987_b1a5.jpg&h=681f32e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歷史是不容刪改的。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》統計全球各地的首名確診病人，發現有至少19個國家或地區的首名確診病人，是在武漢封城前或封城後14天內出現並來自武漢的。<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體根據民航數據，發現自去年12月30日至武漢封城前，已有數十萬名武漢人乘搭飛機前往世界各地，中國境內的主要目的地為北京、廣州和成都，前往廣東的有12.4萬人；國際航線方面，在該段時間內直飛香港的武漢人有超過7,000人、台灣的有7,500人，而前往泰國曼谷的則有超過2萬人，也令曼谷在1月13日出現首宗中國境外確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港、台灣及疫情十分嚴重的意大利首宗確診個案都是來自封城前的武漢，本港的為一名39歲男旅客，他先從武漢到深圳北，再從深圳北坐高鐵到西九龍站，被發現發燒後送院，故此除了可統計的直飛航班，武漢封城前或許有不少感染者，以各種方法離開武漢，並令病毒蔓延。值得提及的是，本港除了首宗確診個案，在1月29日確診的一對武漢老夫婦，也被發現為1月22日從武漢乘搭飛機抵港，並在發燒後沒有即時求醫，而是前往不同酒店要求入住。無獨有偶，確診人數超過十萬人的意大利首名確診病人也是來自武漢，1月22日抵意。<br />\n<br />\n有研究指，武漢封城讓中國減少70萬感染人口，不過，中國官方自12月起發現他們聲稱的「不明原因肺炎病毒」，延至1月20日才承認有人傳人風險，1月23日用上強硬手段封閉武漢，這段時間，又讓全球多少個國家、多少人口受到感染？"},{"pid":"c1852d5aec07ec6144a17c4477814e6df59b1958","tid":1962181,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d08ee0dc51fa43fd6b485e5af300b75cbbe6e48","tid":1962181,"uid":220985,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:59:03.000Z","msg":"如果有果到嘅journal source 就好"},{"pid":"a2180971b3c71c69d4dbf0890e9ce7f06350a558","tid":1962181,"uid":78470,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"f31234d86a550ec38c6c335fef0007b609433aad","tid":1962181,"uid":118120,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"武漢吊打全球<br />\n一個地級市玩殘多國"},{"pid":"d7d8e5104a8674235daa8c4f3c59d7b6c4662924","tid":1962181,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"963762fd27e0522ea1dbbb1cfd638155cad5b9d0","tid":1962181,"uid":225130,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:02:49.000Z","msg":"美國左膠:racism!"},{"pid":"fb18b63a2f0889506e02cbf467596abe509b2ac4","tid":1962181,"uid":79117,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:03:40.000Z","msg":"好的，中國武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853ac1eef519b286b106c1d71744558d372b449a","tid":1962181,"uid":198467,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"推到有source, 英文version,Twitter link"},{"pid":"423d5c739fd74b2e400626cae300f1a0ac5c1864","tid":1962181,"uid":198467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"